fields.name: uniqueHomePage
fields.label: Homepage is unique
fields.description: change to false to add sidebar to homepage

fields.name: docSections
fields.label: Doc Sections
fields.description: use the setting to set multiple docs directories.

fields.name: EnableDarkMode
fields.label: Enable Dark Mode
fields.description: set to false to disable darkmode by default # user will still have the option to use dark mode

fields.name: codeMaxLines
fields.label: Maximum lines in snippet
fields.description: sets the maximum number of lines per codeblock. The codeblock will however be scrollable and expandable.

fields.name: showLineNumbers
fields.label: Show line numbers
fields.description: show/hide line numbers by default. Switch to `true` if you'd rather have them on.

fields.name: iconsPath
fields.label: Icons path
fields.description: By default the template will look for icons under the `icons` directory

fields.name: enableCopyright
fields.label: Enable copyright
fields.description: Defaults to 'true'. Enable copyRight Footer Stamp. Takes in attribution.

fields.name: enable
fields.label: Enable Algolia search
fields.description: if not enabled search will default to fusejs
